name: Chemistry 172 Notes
body:
### Welcome
This is the landing page for the LaTeX notes on the Chemistry 172 course in Northwestern university. To get started, download the zip file for the .tex and compiled pdf file or visit the github page to view the pdf file online. Please note that the notes are as-is and are intended to provide all of the required information in the course in a concise manner. It is intended that these notes serve as references rather than an absolute guide to the course.

### Contact
Please submit support tickets on the github page if there is any incorrect information or information you would like to add.
